docs {
  # Disconnect/Unlink Slack User
  
  Unlinks a Slack user from their Inkeep account.
  
  **Auth:** Session token
  
  **Endpoint:** `POST /work-apps/slack/users/disconnect`
  
  **Body (provide one of these combinations):**
  - `slackUserId` + `slackTeamId` - Direct unlink by Slack user (preferred)
  - `userId` - Inkeep user ID (will look up connection)
  - `connectionId` - Direct connection ID delete
  
  **Returns:**
  - `success: true` on successful unlink
  - Error 404 if no connection found
}
